The/DT salt/NN will/MD pull/VB out/RP the/DT water/NN from/IN the/DT Radish/NNP ./.
Squeeze/VB out/RB and/CC discard/VB all/DT of/IN the/DT water/NN from/IN the/DT Radish/NNP ./.
Add/VB Cilantro/NNP ,/, Green/NNP Chilies/NNP and/CC Carom/NNP Seeds/NNS to/TO the/DT Radish/NNP ./.
Mix/NNP well/RB ./.
Divide/VB dough/NN into/IN approx/NN 8/CD balls/NNS ./.
