Roll/NNP out/IN one/CD dough/JJ ball/NN into/IN a/DT small/JJ disc/NN using/VBG dry/JJ flour/NN to/TO prevent/VB sticking/NN ./.
Place/VB one/CD portion/NN of/IN Radish/JJ mixture/NN in/IN the/DT center/NN of/IN the/DT disc/NN ./.
Wrap/NNP the/DT dough/NN around/IN the/DT Radish/JJ mixture/NN to/TO form/VB a/DT ball/NN ./.
